            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01FAnV1WHGn3k9ozuffbVoNz\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"Great start! I can see you're building something really compelling here. You've identified a real pain point - men in their 50s who've been told they're too old AND have no fitness experience. Now I need to understand exactly HOW your program solves this. Can you finish that thought and tell me: what makes your fitness program specifically designed to overcome these barriers? What's different about your approach compared to generic fitness programs?\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"My program uses beginner-friendly exercises that don't require prior experience, with modifications for aging joints and recovery needs\\\",\\n    \\\"I focus on building confidence first through small wins, then gradually increase intensity to prove age is just a number\\\",\\n    \\\"My program combines personalized coaching with a community of other men in their 50s so they don't feel alone in their journey\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"Help me understand the core mechanism of how your program actually solves their problems.\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2542,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":228,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
