            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 2134,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01LH2HeCRBHGM958V6zzSATx\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Excellent! 🎉 **You've completed your brainstorm!** \\n\\nI now have everything I need to create a compelling landing page for Friend of the Pod. Here's what we're working with:\\n\\n✅ **Your Idea:** AI-powered podcast matchmaking that solves the \\\"needle in a haystack\\\" problem  \\n✅ **Your Audience:** Growing independent podcast hosts (10K-500K listeners) frustrated with manual guest sourcing  \\n✅ **Your Solution:** Minutes instead of hours to find perfect-fit guests, with measurable results  \\n✅ **Your Social Proof:** 8+ years founder experience, 1,000+ successful matches, 92% satisfaction rate, featured in Podcast Magazine\\n\\n---\\n\\nNow you have **two options**:\\n\\n**Option 1: Personalize Your Brand (Optional)**\\n- Upload your logo and choose brand colors\\n- Add social links (Twitter, Instagram, LinkedIn, etc.)\\n- Upload custom images for the page\\n- Takes just a few minutes if you have assets ready\\n\\n**Option 2: Build Right Away**\\n- Skip personalization and hit \\\"Build My Site\\\" to see your landing page\\n- We'll apply smart defaults that look great\\n- You can always customize later!\\n\\nWhat sounds good to you? 🚀\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"Amazing work! You've given me everything I need to create a compelling landing page for Friend of the Pod. Now you have two options:\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"Personalize the design (optional): Upload your logo, pick brand colors, add social links, or choose specific images. Check out the Brand Personalization panel on the left.\\\",\\n    \\\"Build right away: Skip personalization for now and hit 'Build My Site' to see your page. You can always customize later!\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"What sounds good to you?\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\