            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1973,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01As9yxTmM5jgrNFXsMcNbLo\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"helpMe\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"Perfect! Let me help you get specific about who you're selling to and what keeps them up at night.\\\",\\n  \\\"template\\\": \\\"**1. Who are they?**\\\\n[Job title/role] at [company size/type], who [specific context about their work or situation]\\\\n\\\\n**2. What's their main pain point?**\\\\nThey spend [time/effort] on [specific task], which [emotional impact: frustrating, exhausting, etc.]\\\\n\\\\n**3. What are they actually trying to achieve?**\\\\nThey want to [specific outcome], so they can [bigger goal or benefit]\\\\n\\\\n**4. Why doesn't what they're doing now work?**\\\\n[Current approach] doesn't work because [specific limitation]\\\\n\\\\n---\\\\n\\\\n**Fill this in for your primary audience (podcast hosts):**\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"**1. Who are they?** Podcast hosts running shows with 5K-500K listeners, who are constantly looking for fresh content ideas and interesting guests to keep their audience engaged.\\\\n\\\\n**2. What's their main pain point?** They spend 10+ hours per week searching for guests through LinkedIn, Twitter, and email outreach, which is exhausting and pulls them away from actual content creation and promotion.\\\\n\\\\n**3. What are they actually trying to achieve?** They want to book quality guests consistently, so they can maintain a regular publishing schedule and grow their audience without burning out.\\\\n\\\\n**4. Why doesn't what they're doing now work?** Manual searching is slow, hit-or-miss, and they often end up with guests who don't fit their show's vibe or audience.\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2850,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":404,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
