            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1368,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01W2u45ZawPNLgyWpqycWSzM\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Excellent! That's powerful social proof—10k+ creators, a concrete case study showing time savings AND results (viral episodes), plus your credible founder story from Spotify and Apple Podcasts. That's exactly what builds trust.\\n\\nNow, let's talk about the **look and feel** of your landing page. This is about the visual design and overall vibe.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"What's the look and feel you want for your landing page? Think about the visual style, tone, and overall impression you want to make on podcast hosts visiting your site.\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"Modern and sleek (minimalist design, bold typography, tech-forward feel)\\\",\\n    \\\"Warm and approachable (friendly colors, conversational tone, community-focused)\\\",\\n    \\\"Professional and premium (sophisticated design, high-end aesthetic, enterprise-grade)\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"What vibe resonates most with your audience of podcast hosts?\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3083,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":227,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
