            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1267,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01SRG837TVDea674uzbbeBDo\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I'd be happy to help you create compelling Google Ads copy! However, I need some information about your business first.\\n\\nCould you please provide the following details:\\n\\n1. **Business Name & Type**: What is your business called, and what industry/service are you in?\\n2. **Primary Service/Product**: What are you mainly selling or offering?\\n3. **Target Audience**: Who are your ideal customers?\\n4. **Key Benefits/Unique Selling Points**: What makes your business stand out?\\n5. **Primary Keywords**: What keywords are most important for your ads?\\n6. **Call-to-Action**: What do you want customers to do? (e.g., call, book, purchase, get a quote)\\n7. **Any Special Offers**: Do you have promotions, discounts, or limited-time offers?\\n\\nOnce you provide this information, I'll generate 6 compelling headlines and 4 descriptions optimized for Google Ads!\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1910,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":212,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
