            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1511,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_013cq9sUWsTVEcNQx4cRFmTN\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Let's start building your ad! I drafted a few headlines and descriptions that meet Google's requirements. Google will mix and match them to find what performs best. We can tailor them together to make them feel just right for you.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"headlines\\\": [\\n    \\\"Find Meeting Times Instantly\\\",\\n    \\\"Stop Scheduling Back-and-Forth\\\",\\n    \\\"Meetings Across Time Zones\\\",\\n    \\\"Your Team's Scheduling Problem\\\",\\n    \\\"Automate Meeting Coordination\\\",\\n    \\\"Save Hours on Calendar Sync\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"descriptions\\\": [\\n    \\\"Connect calendars, set preferences, done. We find times that work for everyone instantly. Join 2,000+ teams.\\\",\\n    \\\"Cut meeting coordination by 80%. TechCorp saves 15 hours weekly. See how distributed teams win.\\\",\\n    \\\"Tired of endless Slack threads? Let us handle scheduling. Click yes, problem solved.\\\",\\n    \\\"Optimal meeting times across continents. No more timezone confusion. Start your free trial today.\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nHow do these feel? I can adjust the tone, focus on different benefits, or create variations if you'd like to test different angles!\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2437,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":269,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
