            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1461,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_014ThS51YS4BRosRvm7vfKtQ\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Let's start building your ad! I drafted a few headlines and descriptions that meet Google's requirements. Google will mix and match them to find what performs best. We can tailor them together to make them feel just right for you.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"headlines\\\": [\\n    \\\"Find Meeting Times Instantly\\\",\\n    \\\"Schedule Across Time Zones\\\",\\n    \\\"One Click, Perfect Meeting Time\\\",\\n    \\\"Stop Wasting Time Scheduling\\\",\\n    \\\"Instant Team Availability Match\\\",\\n    \\\"Smart Scheduling for Remote Teams\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"descriptions\\\": [\\n    \\\"Connect your calendar and let AI find the perfect time. Your team approves in seconds, not days.\\\",\\n    \\\"Used by 2,000+ teams. Cut scheduling time by 80%. Start your free trial today.\\\",\\n    \\\"No more Slack threads. No more back-and-forth. Just optimal meeting times instantly.\\\",\\n    \\\"Save 15 hours weekly on coordination. See why distributed teams choose us. Try free now.\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nHow do these feel? I can adjust any of them—just let me know which ones resonate and which ones need tweaking!\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2491,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":260,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
