            "size": 1528,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01WBjWncoocjHT3gzeE4Uk8B\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Let's start building your ad! I drafted a few headlines and descriptions that meet Google's requirements. Google will mix and match them to find what performs best. We can tailor them together to make them feel just right for you.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"headlines\\\": [\\n    \\\"Stop Wasting Time Scheduling\\\",\\n    \\\"Find Meeting Times Instantly\\\",\\n    \\\"Teams Love Our Scheduler\\\",\\n    \\\"Scheduling Made Effortless\\\",\\n    \\\"50% Less Scheduling Stress\\\",\\n    \\\"One Click, Perfect Meeting Time\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"descriptions\\\": [\\n    \\\"Connect calendars, set preferences, done. We find times that work for everyone across time zones instantly.\\\",\\n    \\\"2,000+ teams save 15 hours weekly. Let us handle the scheduling chaos—your team just clicks yes.\\\",\\n    \\\"Tired of endless Slack threads? Get optimal meeting times in seconds. Try it free today.\\\",\\n    \\\"Cut coordination time by 80%. Distributed teams trust us to eliminate scheduling headaches.\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nWhat do you think? Feel free to let me know which headlines or descriptions resonate with you, or if you'd like me to adjust the tone, focus, or messaging!\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2468,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":271,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
