        "response": {
          "bodySize": 1555,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1555,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_015m1UkqbdQSoNsypuV9C4xz\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Let's start building your ad! I drafted a few headlines and descriptions that meet Google's requirements. Google will mix and match them to find what performs best. We can tailor them together to make them feel just right for you.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"headlines\\\": [\\n    \\\"Find Meeting Times Instantly\\\",\\n    \\\"Stop Scheduling Back-and-Forth\\\",\\n    \\\"Meetings Across Time Zones?\\\",\\n    \\\"80% Less Coordination Time\\\",\\n    \\\"Smart Scheduling for Teams\\\",\\n    \\\"One Click, Perfect Meeting Time\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"descriptions\\\": [\\n    \\\"Connect calendars, set preferences, done. We find times that work for everyone instantly. Try free today.\\\",\\n    \\\"Trusted by 2,000+ distributed teams. Cut meeting coordination by 80%. See how TechCorp saves 15 hours weekly.\\\",\\n    \\\"Tired of endless Slack threads? Our AI suggests optimal times across continents in seconds. Get started now.\\\",\\n    \\\"No more timezone headaches. Share availability once, let us handle the rest. Join teams saving hours weekly.\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nHow do these feel? I can adjust the tone, focus on different benefits, or create variations if you'd like to test different angles!\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2383,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":279,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
