            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1523,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01SErKWjpcEUjv71Hhquywqa\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Let's start building your ad! I drafted a few headlines and descriptions that meet Google's requirements. Google will mix and match them to find what performs best. We can tailor them together to make them feel just right for you.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"headlines\\\": [\\n    \\\"Stop the scheduling chaos\\\",\\n    \\\"Meeting times in seconds\\\",\\n    \\\"Your calendar, solved\\\",\\n    \\\"No more timezone headaches\\\",\\n    \\\"Meetings that actually work\\\",\\n    \\\"Scheduling made effortless\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"descriptions\\\": [\\n    \\\"Connect your calendar and let us find the perfect time. Your team approves in one click. Try free today.\\\",\\n    \\\"2,000+ teams cut coordination time by 80%. See how distributed companies save hours every week.\\\",\\n    \\\"Tired of endless scheduling threads? Get optimal meeting times across all time zones instantly.\\\",\\n    \\\"Stop playing calendar Tetris. We handle timezone conflicts so your team can focus on work.\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nWhat do you think? Feel free to tell me which headlines and descriptions resonate with you, or let me know if you'd like me to adjust the tone, focus, or messaging!\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2496,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":260,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
