            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1466,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_015DG5RzGkTrtFwz1ZDyT8a1\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Let's start building your ad! I drafted a few headlines and descriptions that meet Google's requirements. Google will mix and match them to find what performs best. We can tailor them together to make them feel just right for you.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"headlines\\\": [\\n    \\\"Find Meeting Times Instantly\\\",\\n    \\\"Stop Scheduling Back-and-Forth\\\",\\n    \\\"Meetings Across Time Zones?\\\",\\n    \\\"Save 15 Hours Weekly\\\",\\n    \\\"Scheduling Made Simple\\\",\\n    \\\"Your Team Clicks Yes\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"descriptions\\\": [\\n    \\\"Connect calendars, set preferences, done. We find times that work for everyone instantly.\\\",\\n    \\\"Used by 2,000+ teams. Cut coordination time by 80%. See why distributed companies choose us.\\\",\\n    \\\"Tired of endless Slack threads? Get optimal meeting times in seconds. Try free today.\\\",\\n    \\\"TechCorp saves 15 hours weekly on scheduling alone. Join teams cutting coordination time by 80%.\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nHow do these feel? I can adjust the tone, focus on different benefits, or create variations if you'd like to test different angles!\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2385,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":263,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
