            "size": 1548,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_018CoXEvFCexniP4GdNJ3MYG\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Let's start building your ad! I drafted a few headlines and descriptions that meet Google's requirements. Google will mix and match them to find what performs best. We can tailor them together to make them feel just right for you.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"headlines\\\": [\\n    \\\"Stop the Scheduling Chaos\\\",\\n    \\\"Meeting Times That Actually Work\\\",\\n    \\\"No More Calendar Ping-Pong\\\",\\n    \\\"Find Times Across Time Zones\\\",\\n    \\\"Your Team's Scheduling Problem: Solved\\\",\\n    \\\"Meetings Coordinated in Seconds\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"descriptions\\\": [\\n    \\\"Connect your calendar and let AI find the perfect meeting time. Your team just clicks yes. Try free today.\\\",\\n    \\\"2,000+ distributed teams save 15 hours weekly. Stop endless Slack threads about scheduling.\\\",\\n    \\\"Eliminate back-and-forth coordination. Instant optimal times across continents. Get started now.\\\",\\n    \\\"Tired of scheduling nightmares? We handle timezone conflicts so you don't have to. Learn more.\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nWhat do you think? Feel free to let me know which headlines or descriptions resonate with you, or if you'd like me to adjust the tone, focus, or messaging!\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2493,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":280,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
